{"tid":1754552,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"取消咗個sem真係好撚悶 大家有咩做?","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T17:08:01.000Z","uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b157cc774c0a80c81a02aaa8720bbf06f5783c","tid":1754552,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"大家好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先係呀開始講之前 我要多謝黎明行動手足, 仲有全部投票俾民主嘅人。 某程度上我都有參與過呢啲活動。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想知有冇人同我一樣學校嗰個sem取消咗or變咗網上平台 然後覺得好撚悶?<br />\n<br />\n依家我有好多時間但係實在有太多時間 唔知有咩做好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知我啲天才level 功課超撚快做曬 仲要係光速咁樣做曬, 啲group project基本上又取消曬唔撚使同我班豬隊友一齊carry佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗集會活動發夢返教會之外 我呢幾個禮拜都冇乜嘢做  (除非你計單機散步係一個活動)<br />\n<br />\n識親嘅人又喺度做嗰啲part time (屌邊撚個會返part time畀人點到陀陀擰呀), 但我本人因為養得起自己夠錢交學費所以就冇諗住做part time <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係做緊part time就喺度溫緊書 (asso 係咪真係咁難?) 唔係溫緊書就喺度拍緊拖 次次叫你哋出嚟你哋都話好撚忙 餵大佬呀出來食個飯唔係好嘥時間啫<br />\n<br />\n咁其實你哋呢排有乜撚嘢做呢 <br />\n<br />\nOh and 聖誕節又到喇 大家有乜嘢打算呢 屌你老母我又要喺屋企hea, 又要行街嗰陣受苦 見到咁撚多人同自己友出街 同伴侶出街 唯獨係我 我屌曬你哋老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ab78970906c8146d19f82d2ef749ccacb609a0","tid":1754552,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:02:18.000Z","msg":"玩 Twitter Reddit IG FB 仲可以發夢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=bd561f0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSen. Marco Rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=1930e44e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&h=2dc87735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Rick Scott<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=5d6b219b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&h=291b9b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Marsha Blackburn<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=3f13f0b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&h=03c18e02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496</a><br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅tweet請入bot搵<br />\n<br />\n（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a>"},{"pid":"3a2cffe669d7e092d9360f5ee3ecf0ff76401b0